delete.description:
This method expects an array of question keys and entity type.

Entity type:

Codes - removes applied codes from questions responses;

QualityCodes - removes quality codes from questions responses;

Responses - removes questions responses;

Question - removes questons;

Response will contain information about result of operation for each of handled questions.
 
If errorMessage is null it means that question/its items succeccfully deleted without error(s).

DeleteQuestionsBatchRequest.description:
Request contains array of question keys which should be handled. 
Entity type determines which items should be removed:
Codes - removes applied codes from questions responses;
QualityCodes - removes quality codes from questions responses;
Responses - removes questions responses;
Question - removes questons;
